@api_host = http://localhost:7071

### Upload PDF Document
POST {{api_host}}/api/upload
Accept: */*
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=Boundary

--Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ../../data/support.pdf
--Boundary--

