### Create a new question
POST {{api_host}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    {
      "content": "How to Search and Book Rentals?",
      "role": "user"
    }
  ],
  "stream": true,
  "context": {},
  "session_state": null
}

### Retrieve PDF document
GET {{api_host}}/api/documents/test.pdf
